data.description: Welcome to a rare find! This property encompasses a sprawling 2.2-acre parcel of land, The centerpiece of this expansive estate is a meticulously crafted 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home. A standout feature of this property is the inclusion of a sizable hangar, that has its own well water, septic and electric and has its own car lift,perfect for boat or car enthusiasts or those with a need for substantial storage space. Additionally, there is an RV port. The convenience of an accessory dwelling unit adds an extra layer of flexibility, whether for guests, extended family, or potential rental income.This real estate gem is not only a comfortable residence but also presents a lucrative investment opportunity. With the land zoned for agricultural use, the possibilities are vast.
